# ============================================================================ #
# GameGuard .gitignore
# 原则：代码 + 文档 + 可 review 的配置进 git；运行产物 / 缓存 / 密钥不进 git
# ============================================================================ #

# --- 密钥 / 环境配置 --------------------------------------------------------
# .env 里有 API key，绝对不能提交
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
# 允许 example 作为模板进 git
!.env.example

# --- Python 产物 -----------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

# setuptools / pip 安装产物
*.egg-info/
*.egg
build/
dist/
wheels/
pip-wheel-metadata/

# --- 测试 / 类型 / Lint 缓存 ------------------------------------------------
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.hypothesis/          # hypothesis shrinking DB，每次跑会变
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/
coverage.xml
*.cover
.tox/
.nox/

# --- GameGuard 运行产物 -----------------------------------------------------
# artifacts/ 下是每次跑产生的 trace / snapshot / report / suite.json
# 保留目录结构（.gitkeep）方便新 clone 能直接跑
artifacts/traces/*
artifacts/snapshots/*
artifacts/reports/*
artifacts/regress/*
artifacts/suite.json
artifacts/*.json
!artifacts/**/.gitkeep

# LLM 磁盘缓存（content-addressed）。本地跑有用，push 远端无意义
.cache/
.llm_cache/

# --- 虚拟环境 --------------------------------------------------------------
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
# conda env 本身不在仓库里（environment.yml 已声明），但以防万一
.conda/

# --- IDE / 编辑器 -----------------------------------------------------------
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.project
.pydevproject

# --- Jupyter ---------------------------------------------------------------
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb_checkpoints

# --- macOS / Windows / Linux 系统文件 ---------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- 私人笔记（如果你在项目里随手写） --------------------------------------
# 面试准备时的个人笔记，避免误推上去
NOTES.md
notes.md
scratch/
TODO.local.md

# --- drawio 自动备份 -------------------------------------------------------
*.bkp
*.drawio.bkp

# --- Eval 运行产物 ---
# evals/ 代码进 git；但每个 eval 的 runtime artifacts 在 artifacts/evals/ 下
artifacts/evals/
